<p align="justify"><span style="font-weight: bold">29th June 2010:</span> Critical Design Review of Structures Sub-System successfully completed. The review was presented by Anirudh. Prof Sudhakar, Prof Arya and Prof Joshi were present. The structures simulations have been completed. </p>
